OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781678874
OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FBy Multimedia Producer Connor Parker
OL,8,FWorld Cup giants Spain were the heavy
OL,9,Ffavourites to win their opening game,
OL,10,Fbut they were stopped in their tracks
OL,11,Fby Cape Verde and their 40-year-old
OL,12,Fgoalkeeper.
OL,14,FIt was Josinar Dias's (also known as
OL,15,FVozinha) first World Cup, and his
OL,16,Fheroic seven saves kept the game 0-0,
OL,17,Fdespite Spain completely dominating
OL,18,Fthe match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
