OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781678874
OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FSpain is ranked second in the world
OL,7,Fbehind Argentina and is one of the
OL,8,Ffavourites to win the tournament.
OL,10,FCape Verde, a small island nation of
OL,11,Fthe coast of West Africa with a
OL,12,Fpopulation of under 500,000, is ranked
OL,13,F67th and is playing in the World Cup
OL,14,Ffor the first time this year.
OL,16,FDraws are rarely celebrated in
OL,17,Ffootball, but for Cape Verde, not
OL,18,Flosing to Spain has been seen as a
OL,19,Fvictory, and Vozinha has become an
OL,20,Fovernight celebrity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
