OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781678874
OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FWho is Vozinha?
OL,8,FVozinha began his career in 2011
OL,9,Fplaying for clubs in Cape Verde before
OL,10,Fbeing signed to teams in Angola,
OL,11,FMoldova and Portugal.
OL,13,FHe has played for his national team
OL,14,Fsince 2012 and was called up to join
OL,15,Fthe World Cup squad when they
OL,16,Fqualified for the tournament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
