PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781678874
OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FAt 40 years and 12 days old, he is the
OL,7,Foldest player to feature in a nation's
OL,8,Ffirst World Cup match and the ninth
OL,9,Foldest player to ever play in the
OL,10,Ftournament.
OL,12,FThe word "vozinha" is Portuguese for
OL,13,F"little grandmother," and the
OL,14,Fgoalkeeper said he was given the
OL,15,Fnickname by older kids who would beat
OL,16,Fhim on the soccer field and then
OL,17,Flaugh, saying he was going home to
OL,18,Fcomplain to his grandparents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781678874
OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FYears later, he took on the nickname
OL,7,Fafter someone else in his club also
OL,8,Fhad the same first name, Josimar.
OL,10,FMan of the match
OL,12,FAfter the match, Vozinha won the
OL,13,FSuperior Player of the Match Award for
OL,14,Fhis performance.
OL,16,FSpain made 27 shots, with almost the
OL,17,Fentire game being played in Cape
OL,18,FVerde's half of the pitch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
