OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781678874
OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FSeven of those shots were on target,
OL,7,Fbut expertly saved from hitting the
OL,8,Fback of the net by Vozinha.
OL,10,FEven the late entrance of FC Barcelona
OL,11,Fsuperstar Lamine Yamal could not break
OL,12,FVozinha or Cape Verde's defence.
OL,14,FAs the final whistle blew, Vozinha
OL,15,Fhunched over near his net and cried
OL,16,Fbefore being embraced by his teammates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
