OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FVozinha said he was overcome by
OL,7,Femotions thinking about his loved ones
OL,8,Fwho were unable to see his finest
OL,9,Fperformance: his grandparents who had
OL,10,Fraised him, and his mother.
OL,12,FHis grandparents died a few years ago,
OL,13,Fand his mother had been unable to
OL,14,Fgather the money in time to secure a
OL,15,Fvisa to enter the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
