OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FCape Verde is among 50 countries whose
OL,7,Fcitizens face bonds of over #10,000 to
OL,8,Fsecure a US visa, part of President
OL,9,FDonald Trump's broader crackdown on
OL,10,Ftravellers from countries that
OL,11,Fofficials said had high rates of visa
OL,12,Foverstays.
OL,14,FThis was briefly suspended for Cape
OL,15,FVerde and four other World Cup
OL,16,Fnations, but critics said the
OL,17,Fsuspension came too late for fans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
