OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781678874
OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,F"I work all my life for this, for this
OL,7,Fmoment, for this dream," Vozinha said.
OL,8,F"A lot of generations in the past
OL,9,F(dreamed of) this day, but they did
OL,10,Fnot achieve it. And now the dream
OL,11,Fcomes true."
OL,13,FOvernight celebrity
OL,15,FIt was not just match officials who
OL,16,Fnoticed his performance. Brazilian
OL,17,FYouTuber CazeTV launched a campaign
OL,18,Fafter the game to get Vozinha to one
OL,19,Fmillion followers on Instagram to
OL,20,Fcelebrate his performance.
OL,26,@qD@ApmqD@Lpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
