OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781678874
OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FSoon after, he posted a picture of
OL,7,Fhimself with his team, saying: "A
OL,8,Fdream come true! Representing Cape
OL,9,FVerde on the biggest stage in world
OL,10,Ffootball is an indescribable honour.
OL,11,FWords fail me... only pride,
OL,12,Fgratitude, and responsibility."
OL,14,FHe also made another post in which he
OL,15,Fcalled his rise in followers "loco"
OL,16,F(crazy).
OL,18,FCape Verde defender Steven Moreira
OL,19,Fsaid he and his teammates like to
OL,20,Ftease Vozinha about his age.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
