OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781678874
OL,3,CWho is Vozinha, Cape Verde's 40-year-
OL,4,Cold goalkeeper who stunned Spain?
OL,6,FHe said he was proud of the keeper,
OL,7,Fcalling him a "big legend" who had a
OL,8,F"crazy game" and showed that age
OL,9,Fdoesn't matter.
OL,11,FDefender Pico Lopes said: "He lives
OL,12,Fand breathes Cape Verde.
OL,14,F"He's always on us to keep us on time.
OL,15,FBut that's what he does. He pushes us
OL,16,Fto be better. And you saw it today, he
OL,17,Fleads by example."
